Impact of HIV infection on aging and immune status.

Blanco JR(1), Negredo E(2), Bernal E(3), Blanco J(4)(5).

Author information:
(1)Servicio de Enfermedades Infecciosas, Hospital Universitario San Pedro- 
Centro De Investigación Biomédica De La Rioja (CIBIR), La Rioja, Spain.
(2)Lluita Contra La Sida Foundation, Germans Trias I Pujol University Hospital, 
Badalona, Spain. Centre for Health and Social Care Research (CESS), Faculty of 
Medicine, University of Vic - Central University of Catalonia (Uvic - UCC), 
