Partial Response and Stable Disease Correlate with Positive Outcomes in 
Atezolizumab-treated Patients with Advanced Urinary Tract Carcinoma.

Bedke J(1), Merseburger AS(2), Loriot Y(3), Castellano D(4), Choy E(5), Duran 
I(6), Rosenberg JE(7), Petrylak DP(8), Dreicer R(9), Perez-Gracia JL(10), 
